WEBVTT

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:31.254
and graze all around them,

00:06:31.278 --> 00:06:35.356
without having to actually bother
with the effort of moving their body.

00:06:35.380 --> 00:06:37.333
(Laughter)

00:06:38.292 --> 00:06:41.926
It also means that they are
surprisingly good swimmers.

00:06:41.950 --> 00:06:44.415
Sloths can bob along in water

00:06:44.439 --> 00:06:47.704
three times faster
than they can move on land,

00:06:47.728 --> 00:06:49.698
kept afloat by ...

00:06:49.722 --> 00:06:51.260
trapped wind.

00:06:51.284 --> 00:06:53.346
(Laughter)

00:06:53.370 --> 00:06:54.544
So --

00:06:54.568 --> 00:06:55.569
(Laughter)

00:06:55.593 --> 00:06:59.504
sloths are the only mammal that we know of
that don't do flatulence.

00:06:59.528 --> 00:07:01.210
When they need to expel gas,